1) Create GKE Cluster from Cloud Shell or Console:-
   gcloud container clusters create cicd-cluster(Cluster name) --machine-type=g1-small(choose the machine image) --num-nodes=1(choose no.of nodes you required) --zone=northamerica-northeast2(choose the region)
2) Deploy some sample Docker Images.
3) Create Load Balancer based service.
4)Create Source Code Repos.
5) Add Python code, DockerFile, Cloudbuild.yaml
6) Cloudbuild.yaml consists:
    a) Clone repo
    b) Build Image
    c) Push Image
    d) Update new image
7) Create Cloud Build Trigger
